sentences.english: Dazu Rock Carvings in 1999 was inscribed on the World Heritage List.
sentences.chinese: 大足石刻1999年被列入世界文化遗产名录。

sentences.english: Dazu County, located in the southeast of Sichuan province, is 271 kilometres away from Chengdu and 163 kilometres away from Chongqing.
sentences.chinese: 大足县在重庆市的西北，县城距重庆百余公里。

sentences.english: The Dazu Stone Carving is World-famous.
sentences.chinese: 大足石刻是世界闻名的。

sentences.english: China travel, Chongqing Dazu Cliff Rock Carvings, Baoding Mountain.
sentences.chinese: 中国旅游，重庆大足石刻崖，保定山。

sentences.english: In Dazu County, Mr Long is an authority on bees and generating higher amounts of honey.
sentences.chinese: 在大足县，龙先生是养蜂专家，蜂蜜产量高于同行。

sentences.english: British Columbia makes it illegal for anyone to kill a sasquatch.
sentences.chinese: 在不列颠哥伦比亚省，杀死大足野人是犯法的。
